      h3 未回答の質問はありません
  #pills-anserwered.tab-pane.fade[role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-anserwered-tab"]
    = render "shared/questions_list", questions: answered_questions
    - unless answered_questions.present?
      h3 回答済みの質問はありません
